item.description:
So basically I made this utility that asks you if you want to reboot if you run &ldquo;sudo reboot&rdquo; instead of doing it right away. You can install it using bash -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https://go.jontes.page/dar.sh)&quot;
You may also use the bleeding edge with https://go.jontes.page/testdar.sh, but I strongly advice against it. It&rsquo;s full of bugs.
Github: https://github.com/Jontes-Tech/dont-actually-reboot
